Why Redux is used ?  Redux is a js libraty to maintain the state, with redux you can easily manage the state. 

Why Babel ? 
1.Babel is a tool chain that mainly used to convert teh ECMAScript 2015+ code in to backword 
compatable version of javascript in current and older browsers or environments. 
